{"title_page": "Hiroki Sasaki", "text_new": "{{short description|Japanese footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Hiroki Sasaki\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Hiroki Sasaki\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1993|7|17}}\n|birth_place=[[Chiba Prefecture|Chiba]], [[Japan]]\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.79}}\n|position=[[Midfielder]]\n|currentclub=[[Fujieda MYFC]]\n|clubnumber=24\n|youthyears1=2009\u20132011|youthclubs1=[[Kashiwa Reysol]]\n|youthyears2=2012\u20132015|youthclubs2=[[Toin University of Yokohama]]\n|years1=2016\u2013|clubs1=[[Fujieda MYFC]]|caps1=1|goals1=0\n|totalcaps=1|totalgoals=0\n|nationalyears1=|nationalteam1=|nationalcaps1=|nationalgoals1=\n|manageryears1=|managerclubs1=\n|medaltemplates=\n|club-update=\n|nationalteam-update=\n}}\n\n{{Nihongo|'''Hiroki Sasaki'''|\u4f50\u3005\u6728 \u5b8f\u6a39|Sasaki Hiroki|born July 17, 1993}} is a [[Japanese people|Japanese]] [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>[https://data.j-league.or.jp/SFIX04/?player_id=19212 J.League Data Site]</ref> He plays for [[Fujieda MYFC]].\n\n==Career==\nHiroki Sasaki joined [[J3 League]] club [[Fujieda MYFC]] in 2016.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{J.League player|19212}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Sasaki, Hiroki}}\n[[Category:1993 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Toin University of Yokohama alumni]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Chiba Prefecture]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J3 League players]]\n[[Category:Fujieda MYFC players]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-midfielder-1990s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Hiroki Sasaki\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Hiroki Sasaki\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1993|7|17}}\n|birth_place=[[Chiba Prefecture|Chiba]], [[Japan]]\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.79}}\n|position=[[Midfielder]]\n|currentclub=[[Fujieda MYFC]]\n|clubnumber=24\n