{"title_page": "Yuya Nishijima", "text_new": "{{short description|Japanese footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Yuya Nishijima\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Yuya Nishijima\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1995|2|21}}\n|birth_place=[[Yamaguchi Prefecture|Yamaguchi]], [[Japan]]\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.79}}\n|position=[[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n|currentclub=[[Gainare Tottori]]\n|clubnumber=24\n|youthyears1=2010\u20132012|youthclubs1=[[Sanfrecce Hiroshima]]\n|youthyears2=2013\u20132016|youthclubs2=[[Fukuoka University]]\n|years1=2017\u2013|clubs1=[[Gainare Tottori]]|caps1=|goals1=\n|totalcaps=|totalgoals=\n|nationalyears1=|nationalteam1=|nationalcaps1=|nationalgoals1=\n|manageryears1=|managerclubs1=\n|medaltemplates=\n|club-update=\n|nationalteam-update=\n}}\n{{Nihongo|'''Yuya Nishijima'''|\u897f\u5d8b \u6709\u77e2|Nishijima Yuya|born February 21, 1995}} is a [[Japanese people|Japanese]] [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>{{J.League player|23135}}</ref> He plays for [[Gainare Tottori]].\n\n==Career==\nYuya Nishijima joined [[J3 League]] club [[Gainare Tottori]] in 2017.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{J.League player|23135}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Nishijima, Yuya}}\n[[Category:1995 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Fukuoka University alumni]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Yamaguchi Prefecture]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J3 League players]]\n[[Category:Gainare Tottori players]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-defender-1990s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Japanese association football player}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Yuya Nishijima\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Yuya Nishijima\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1995|2|21}}\n|birth_place=[[Yamaguchi Prefecture|Yamaguchi]], [[Japan]]\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.79}}\n|position=[